- System should be able to register dentists
- System should be able to register patients
- System should be able to let dentist sign-in 
- System should allow dentist view listing of their appointments
- System should be able to enroll new Patients
- System should allow patients call-in to request appointments to see a dentist
- System should allow patients request appointment by submitting an online form on the ADS website
- System should be able to send a confirmation email notifying the Patient about appointment
- System should provide information about each Surgery
- System should allow patients sign-in to the system
- System should allow patients to view their appointments, including the information of the dentist who they have been booked
- System should allow patients cancel or change appointments
- System should prevent a Patient from requesting a new appointment if they have an outstanding unpaid bill.
